reviewText: Gift for someone.  He said he loved it.

Good concert and a great look at Zevon on stage. Top notch performance, though what is not top notch is the low def video, and the fact that they omitted the single most energetic cut, "Cadillac Ranch," from this disk.
Awesome show! Just to have a video record of one of his concerts really is amazing! Saw him many times and this brings back lots of memories.
